                        <condition key="deficient">The Ms. is worn.
 The Ms. has been
                           resewn.
 The leather cover is damaged: additional rectangular pieces
                           of leather have been crudely sewn to the spine, to substitute for the
                           portion of the overback which was cut off.
 Most of the fols. are
                           damaged by water (esp. <locus from="53" to="61">53-61</locus>, 126-145),
                           many are cockled.
 ff. 1-13 are damaged by rodents.
 Tears
                           carefully amended on <locus target="#11">11</locus>, 14, 17, 37, 42, 44,
                           81, 83, 85, 86, 87, 134, 148, 154, 163, 167, 186, 189.</condition>
